oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Original wills, Arceneaux, Mrs. Daisy R., 1910 July 01
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An original will of Mrs. Daisy R. Arceneaux, dated May 7th, 1910. Illustrates the first page of the document. The verso cites the probate date of July 1st, 1910 in “WB 37:320, MB 12:445” in the Davidson County Court. Forms part of Record Group 16, Original Wills, 1780-1925.
